{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot depicts an industrial waterfront scene under a cloudy sky. A massive, dark-colored gantry crane dominates the foreground, extending vertically over a dock filled with scrap metal and debris. The crane is composed of a complex lattice structure, with a smaller, bright yellow lifting mechanism suspended beneath. To the right of the main crane is a smaller, yellow crane on a platform, also involved in handling the scrap metal. The dock is constructed of wooden pilings and has various pieces of heavy machinery present.  In the background, a hazy landmass is visible. The water in the foreground is slightly choppy, reflecting the sky and the structures on the dock. The lighting is diffused due to the cloud cover.",
